---
// Email capture via StaticForms - no server required
---
<aside class="my-10 rounded-xl border border-grass-700 bg-grass-50 p-6 md:p-8">
  <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-soil-900 mb-2">The 10-Minute Lawn Edge</h2>
  <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-5">
    One short email each month: what to do to your lawn now, and which kit is actually worth buying.
  </p>
  <form
    action="https://api.staticforms.xyz/submit"
    method="POST"
    class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3"
  >
    <input type="hidden" name="accessKey" value="sf_9e906eb6c00416b9d3354749" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_site" value="thebestmowers.co.uk" />
    <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="TheBestMowers - New subscriber (thebestmowers.co.uk)" />
    <input type="hidden" name="redirectTo" value="https://thebestmowers.co.uk/?subscribed=1" />
    <input type="text" name="honeypot" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
    <label for="ec-email" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
    <input
      id="ec-email"
      type="email"
      name="email"
      required
      placeholder="your@email.com"
      class="flex-1 rounded-md border border-grass-700 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-soil-900 placeholder-slate-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-grass-700 min-h-[44px]"
    />
    <button
      type="submit"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-grass-700 hover:bg-grass-800 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-md min-h-[44px] text-sm whitespace-nowrap"
    >
      Subscribe - it's free
    </button>
  </form>
  <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">No spam. Unsubscribe any time.</p>
</aside>
